<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">加减乘整法，方法一，两数相乘，因数都比整十、整百......略小，可将两乘数相加后减去整十、整百......，再用此数乘以整十、整百......，然后加上整十、整百......分别减去两个因数得到差的乘积，即得其积。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">198×197=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">198×197</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(198+197-200)×200+(200-198)×(200-197)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=195×200+2×3</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=39000+6</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=39006</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>